data.description: Are you looking for a home with lots of space? Then this well-maintained home with a finished basement boasting 5 bedrooms (2 in lower level with egress windows) on a double lot is the perfect one for you. The basement includes a family room featuring a gas log fireplace. Enjoy the nice 3 seasons room to take in the lovely evening sunsets. There is a 2 car attached garage and an additional 3 car detached garage, both fully insulated. Additionally, there are sheds, a covered patio, fenced yard and a fire pit for entertaining family and friends. The Kinetico water softener is owned.
